obabilistic models that can then be invoked against observations, combined, and compared.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>See <a href=\"https:\/\/dx.doi.org\/10.1073\/pnas.2220045120\">our recent publication<\/a> for an of probabilistic methods applied to chemistry.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column has-background is-layout-flow wp-container-core-column-is-layout-2 wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"background-color:#e9f3d9;padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--10);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--10);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--10);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--10)\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-left is-style-default has-body-font-family has-medium-font-size\" style=\"font-style:normal;font-weight:600\"><kbd><code>rp2040hw<\/code><\/kbd><br><a href=\"https:\/\/github.com\/MehrResearch\/rp2040hw\">MehrResearch\/rp2040hw<\/a><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\">This library for the RP2040 microcontroller combines the low-level precision of bare-metal programming with the convenience and interactivity of MicroPython by providing access to most RP2040 hardware registers.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column has-background is-layout-flow wp-container-core-column-is-layout-3 wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"background-color:#e9f3d9;padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--10);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--10);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--10);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--10)\">\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading has-text-align-left is-style-default has-body-font-family has-medium-font-size\" style=\"font-style:normal;font-weight:600\"><code>HacksYStage<\/code><br><a href=\"https:\/\/github.com\/MehrResearch\/HacksYStage\">MehrResearch\/HacksYStage<\/a><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-left\">A very cheap and hacky microscope XY stage powered by old CD\/DVD drives and Arduino.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group alignfull ha